{"tid":1304240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣入] 要求撤控義士有個point值得大講特講","createTime":"2019-07-10T14:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T02:36:51.000Z","uid":62610,"like":88,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a54723d8de22a07a441b263abde735aa0acac139","tid":1304240,"uid":62610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:21:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190630/20716704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F20716704&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3T632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=affc13dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F20716704&h=31fd8b71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190630/20716704</a><br />\n政府成日話特赦/唔檢控係違反法治精神<br />\n其實係有得反駁<br />\n除左67暴動特赦貪污警察同98年胡仙案兩個歷史案例之外<br />\n雜種最近特赦左9類罪犯<br />\n咁政府係咪即係話支那唔係法治社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家諗下可以點扭個point<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3324a978f1d3f6d7a79a7cd6dbcac2ca0ced5c78","tid":1304240,"uid":62610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:22:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3e85a96153aed8e3d1007cc6fea8acfd9bcd746a","tid":1304240,"uid":62610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:23:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4bbc4cdddb9ef3af098de95333b973f8314fb3ce","tid":1304240,"uid":62610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:25:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fcd2e72130908dfa5e7823800c74627464829c5e","tid":1304240,"uid":62610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:26:45.000Z","msg":"我冇野講